<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr />

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: "profile-img" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-alert" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%;">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>A former Air Traffic Controller and Full Stack Developer with a passion for code.
          Always interested in new opportunities to apply my knowledge in Angular, JavaScript, C#,
          SQL, Elixir. I have degrees in both Computer Science and Aerospace and he critical
          thinking and problem solving skills to back them up.</p>

        <p>In my spare time I enjoy training and competing in endurance sport. I'm a
          Boston qualifying marathoner and multiple time Ironman triathlon finisher. A
          lifelong nerd and gamer. A private pilot. I enjoy all aspects of technology,
          building and creating.</p>

        <p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#jobs" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="jobs">
            Job History
          </button>

          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#education" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="education">
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
        <div class="collapse" id="jobs">
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Senior Software Engineer</strong></p>
            <div>Slalom Build</div>
            <div>Sept. 2019 - Present</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Software Engineer</strong></p>
            <div>Slalom Build</div>
            <div>Oct. 2018 - Sept. 2019</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Software Engineer</strong></p>
            <div>Seer Aerospace</div>
            <div>Oct. 2017 - Oct. 2018</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Air Traffic Controller</strong></p>
            <div>Federal Aviation Administration</div>
            <div>Feb. 2008 - Dec. 2016</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </p>

        <p>
        <div class="collapse" id="education">
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Flatiron School</strong></p>
            <div>Full Stack Web Dev</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Middle Tennessee State University</strong></p>
            <div>Bachelor of Science, Aerospace</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <p><strong>Western Kentucky University</strong></p>
            <div>Bachelor of Science, Computer Science</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>